ZH: 我们下次见面找个地方吃饭吧。
EN: Let's find a place to eat together next time we meet.

ZH: 下次不要这样做了，太危险了。
EN: Don't do it like this next time, it's too dangerous.

ZH: 下次我会记得带伞，不会再淋雨了。
EN: I will remember to bring an umbrella next time, so I won't get caught in the rain again.

ZH: 下次你再这样说我就不理你了。
EN: If you say that to me again next time, I will ignore you.

ZH: 下次再给我来一碗这个菜，味道太好了。
EN: Bring me another bowl of this dish next time, it tastes so good.

ZH: 下次再邀请我参加你的生日聚会吧。
EN: Invite me to your birthday party again next time.

ZH: 下次再和我一起去爬山，我非常喜欢这种运动。
EN: Come hiking with me again next time, I really enjoy this activity.

ZH: 下次别忘了给我带点特产，我非常喜欢。
EN: Don't forget to bring me some local specialties next time, I really like them.

ZH: 下次我们去看电影，你想看哪部？
EN: Which movie do you want to watch next time we go to the cinema?

ZH: 下次我们可以尝试一下这家新开的餐厅。
EN: Let's try this newly opened restaurant next time.

ZH: 下次你再打电话给我，我就告诉你答案。
EN: If you call me again next time, I will tell you the answer.

ZH: 下次我会提前一点来的，不会再迟到了。
EN: I will come earlier next time, so I won't be late again.

ZH: 下次别说那么多废话，直接说重点。
EN: Don't talk so much nonsense next time, just get to the point.

ZH: 下次我会把车停在离这里更近的地方。
EN: I will park the car closer next time.

ZH: 下次我会注意时间，不会浪费你的等待。
EN: I will pay attention to the time next time and won't waste your wait.

ZH: 下次我们去的时候，带上相机拍些照片留念。
EN: Bring a camera with us next time we go and take some photos for memories.

ZH: 下次去游泳记得戴上泳帽，不然头发会弄湿。
EN: Remember to wear a swimming cap next time we go swimming, or your hair will get wet.

ZH: 下次我们可以一起去商店逛逛，看看有没有喜欢的东西。
EN: We can go shopping together next time and see if there is anything you like.

ZH: 下次你可以帮我带几个文件吗？我明天要用。
EN: Can you bring me some files next time? I will need them tomorrow.

ZH: 下次我们可以一起去野餐，享受自然的美景。
EN: Let's go on a picnic together next time and enjoy the beauty of nature.
